snippet.title: The Cthulhu Mythos Horror Game, Blood Lily Loop, Opening
snippet.description:
Steam store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2675270/
X: https://twitter.com/i_khaos
Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/SoundingStoneIndieGame

Your bestie seems to be hiding something. There's something about your world that seems odd as well, like it has...secrets. Dive into the Cthulhu Mythos universe of this horror game and witness a "friendship" that rewrites the world.
